{"tid":2206644,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"想學整四川涼麵","createTime":"2020-09-17T15:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T01:52:55.000Z","uid":299802,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4370726fb5506aa8fd795b3337bd216f03e69538","tid":2206644,"uid":299802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T15:06:37.000Z","msg":"之前食過葵廣間四川美味涼麵<br />\n一直都好想自己試下整，但整極都唔啱味<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲可以教路<br />\n<br />\n我本身就咁樣調個醬汁<br />\n鹽         1/4匙<br />\n雞精     1/4匙<br />\n生抽        1匙<br />\n陳醋        1匙<br />\n花椒油 1/2匙<br />\n辣椒油     1匙<br />\n蒜水         1匙<br />\n糖         3/4匙<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4515bed3575eb20e01f09a7c588d1aa72bbc6920","tid":2206644,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T15:16:24.000Z","msg":"師兄D涼麵係邊度買的"},{"pid":"464a8d35f6d836923ba26cf41cccb41fc2ad4e46","tid":2206644,"uid":125210,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T15:30:06.000Z","msg":"加多半茶匙味精就夠味㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83b1f6f5daec133a7192ba4603fca5f836149ea","tid":2206644,"uid":42662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T15:36:20.000Z","msg":"辣椒油應該要用四川個種香辣紅油"},{"pid":"d4715f0e9481c2af93a3737a12949617f0a55ffc","tid":2206644,"uid":299802,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"4515bed3575eb20e01f09a7c588d1aa72bbc6920","tid":2206644,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T15:16:24.000Z","msg":"師兄D涼麵係邊度買的"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T15:54:50.000Z","msg":"我用意粉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該最接近<br />\n吹涼佢之後 撈少少油"},{"pid":"b0acb7f3a8fc93e916fc328854b0e7b4c638de15","tid":2206644,"uid":299802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"464a8d35f6d836923ba26cf41cccb41fc2ad4e46","tid":2206644,"uid":125210,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-