79f94f03efbe195d92b6","tid":2206644,"uid":61384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T17:12:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HpFSi67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHpFSi67.jpg&h=5c794428&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nLiving Plaza"},{"pid":"edfe562315e95ff47aa04ebd4fdf9314230fbbc3","tid":2206644,"uid":299802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d24785aa6e0c740e3484ed07564049f55d5881f4","tid":2206644,"uid":288764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T16:44:07.000Z","msg":"可以自己做辣椒油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細辣椒粉，有籽辣椒粉，芝麻，鹽<br />\n五香粉加唔加就因自己口味<br />\n菜油燒紅後礸落去<br />\n之後撈埋其他材料<br />\n<br />\n蒜水係蒜蓉+鹽+麻油+水？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T01:52:55.000Z","msg":"我蒜水喺顧名思義 認真蒜+水<br />\n蒜切蓉之後 熱水淋落去 <br />\n但見啲大陸人有時會用高湯代替熱水<br />\n<br />\n至於辣椒油<br />\n啲油潑辣椒之前 好似要炸過蔥薑，八角，bay leave 提味<br />\n我就嫌麻煩寧願出去買<br />\n上面有巴打介紹買四川辣椒油先啱使"}]}